si Jiang Xiao Shuai.

177
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:29,480
Pinahihirapan mo lang
ang sarili mo.

178
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:39,520
Tara na.

179
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,480
kamusta na siya?

180
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,680
Hinihintay ko na lang siyang magising.

181
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,040
