202
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,480
Xiao Gang!

203
00:18:21,481 --> 00:18:23,760
Ito ay isang hindi pagkakaunawaan.
kaya kong ipaliwanag.

204
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:36,240
Da Wei.

205
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,960
Xiao Shuai.

206
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:40,560
